data.description: Price Reduction! Assumable VA Loan at 3.75% for qualified buyer. Call for information. Lovely 3 bedroom, 2-1/2 bath home w/ incredible mountain VIEWS, from sunrise to sunset on almost a quarter acre! Tons of space with 2,483 sqft living. Can easily be converted to a 5 bedroom if desired. Open layout with a dreamy kitchen featuring upgraded cabinetry, granite countertops, gas cooktop, double ovens, stainless appliances, subway tiled backsplash, and oversized island with sink. Secondary space downstairs can be used to fit your needs. Soft water system. Luxurious master with walk-in closet. Room for seating area or office. Spa like bath with soaking tub, double vanity and walk-in shower. Enormous Loft. Oversized secondary bathroom. 3 car garage with new door opener. New paint and light fixtures inside and outside. New life proof luxury vinyl plank flooring downstairs. Refrigerator, Washer, and Dryer included. Low HOA. Culdesac lot with open space behind. Spa pad, artificial turf, and cobblestone patio extension. Room to add a pool(currently used as a dog run). Dual cooling with NEW A/C unit for upstairs. Bring your things and move right in! Truly a pride of ownership! Call for your private showing today.
